profile: From premium soil and mulches to any type of aggregate products - we’ve got it all, and we’ll make your gardening projects enjoyable by doing the dirty work for you. We deliver our soil and mulch in conveniently sized bags (50 lbs) and deliver them directly to your gardens. We will even empty the contents of the bags for you. Your customer satisfaction is important to us. We ensure to meet and exceed your expectations with our friendly service, quick and convenient delivery, and quality products.  Visit us at www.dirtcheap.ca
